{{#> layout
  title='Alternatives to Vocably'
  url='/alternatives.html'
}}
  {{#> text-container }}
    <h1 class="py-5">Alternatives to Vocably</h1>

    <p>While working on Vocably, I wanted it to have four features:</p>

    <ol>
      <li>Instant translations</li>
      <li>Review and study on mobile</li>
      <li>Normal forms</li>
      <li>Instant definitions</li>
    </ol>

    <p>I wanted all of these features to be available in the free version, but I failed! There are some alternatives though which have achieved most of these features and are even able to provide a free version.</p>

    <table class="table mb-5">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th scope="col"></th>
          <th scope="col">Translations</th>
          <th scope="col">Study on mobile</th>
          <th scope="col">Definitions</th>
          <th scope="col">Normal forms</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
      {{#each htmlWebpackPlugin.options.alternatives as |alternative|}}
        <tr>
          <td><a href="{{alternative.url}}">{{alternative.name}}</a></td>
          <td class="text-center">{{#if alternative.translations}} <i class="bi-check text-primary"></i>Ô∏è {{^}} <i class="bi bi-x text-danger"></i> {{/if}}</td>
          <td class="text-center">{{#if alternative.mobile}} <i class="bi-check text-primary"></i> {{^}} <i class="bi bi-x text-danger"></i> {{/if}}</td>
          <td class="text-center">{{#if alternative.definitions}} <i class="bi-check text-primary"></i> {{^}} <i class="bi bi-x text-danger"></i> {{/if}}</td>
          <td class="text-center">{{#if alternative.normalForms}} <i class="bi-check text-primary"></i> {{^}} <i class="bi bi-x text-danger"></i> {{/if}}</td>
        </tr>
      {{/each}}
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <p>Also, there are plenty of extensions without a mobile version, and those that let users learn languages by reading content in their first language, but I decided not to post them here.</p>

  {{/text-container}}
{{/layout}}
